      answer: 'Email marketing is worth starting from your very first subscriber because the systems you build (welcome sequence, content templates, lead magnets) serve every future subscriber automatically. However, you will start seeing measurable revenue impact once your list reaches approximately 300 to 500 engaged subscribers. At that size, a product announcement email reaching 25% open rate puts your product in front of 75 to 125 interested buyers \u2014 enough to generate consistent sales with each broadcast. Start building your email systems now regardless of your current subscriber count, because every day you delay is traffic and customers you cannot reach later.',
